{
  "stem": "22652.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And boy, she, she no longer was considered-- you know, she no longer got her extra portion of noodles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, we went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just want to mention that it, it had a little school home with two floors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One had, maybe, like kindergarten through, through fifth and sixth grade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other had seventh grade and up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was so freezing, once in awhile we would get up from our chair and go like this, and jump all over to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were always hungry, always freezing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we went to bed-- we had a nap and the nuns would say, you have a nap, and you won't think of hunger.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I remember always dreaming of food and how hungry I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a period of starvation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, the holidays were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We changed uniforms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had bright uniforms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had a good breakfast, and I think a little meat and a little milk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the festivities, lots of songs and drama plays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And just a feeling of joy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I have to mention that this was a particular Christmas that I had my doll with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother had given me a doll.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was pretty beat up by then, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And people would say, you're a big girl, you still like dolls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I-- that doll was like a baby blanket.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and my doll was nowhere in sight, and I was crying and looking for my doll.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And on Christmas day, at the breakfast table, there was a package.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And when I opened it, it was-- my doll was in it with a whole brand new outfit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The girls and the nun had made the-- a beautiful wardrobe.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
